. cap noisily twowayfeweights E fe_group year d_keeprate, type(feTR) weight(epo
> p) summary_measures
The treatment variable in the regression varies within some group * period cell
> s.
The results in de Chaisemartin, C. and D'Haultfoeuille, X. (2020) apply to two-
> way fixed effects regressions
with a group * period level treatment.
The command will replace the treatment by its average value in each group * per
> iod.
The results below apply to the two-way fixed effects regression with that treat
> ment variable.

